link: R. H. Hardin, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..1000
maple: g := -1+product(1+x^(2*binomial(2*j, j)/(j+1))/(1-x^(binomial(2*j, j)/(j+1))), j = 1 .. 10): gser := series(g, x = 0, 75): seq(coeff(gser, x, n), n = 1 .. 70); # _Emeric Deutsch_, Jun 22 2009
